{"_id":"post-2b081b1a-f657-401d-9673-c5b59510d525","_type":"post","title":"Changelog - June 2021","slug":{"_type":"slug","current":"changelog-06-21"},"body":[{"_key":"1212870e7a75","children":[{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"Welcome to the June edition of our monthly changelog, where we highlight some of our big and small feature releases, user experience changes, and bug fixes!","_key":"1212870e7a750"}],"markDefs":[],"_type":"block","style":"normal"},{"_key":"2c1963324395","children":[{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"We love hearing from you! Please leave any feedback you have ","_key":"2c19633243950"},{"_type":"span","marks":["fcd1cfdc691b"],"text":"here","_key":"2c19633243951"},{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":".","_key":"2c19633243952"}],"markDefs":[{"_key":"fcd1cfdc691b","_type":"link","href":"https://replit.canny.io/general-feedback"}],"_type":"block","style":"normal"},{"_key":"82873d76d553","children":[{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"Features","_key":"82873d76d5530"}],"markDefs":[],"_type":"block","style":"h1"},{"_key":"a10f809243bf","children":[{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"We released the first version of our multiplayer debugger! See the ","_key":"a10f809243bf0"},{"_type":"span","marks":["81b07290e291"],"text":"blog post","_key":"a10f809243bf1"},{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":" for all the details.","_key":"a10f809243bf2"}],"markDefs":[{"_key":"81b07290e291","_type":"link","href":"https://blog.replit.com/multiplayer-debugging"}],"_type":"block","style":"normal","level":1,"listItem":"bullet"},{"_key":"08392594823e","children":[{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"You can now observe other users when multiplaying by clicking on their avatar.","_key":"08392594823e0"}],"markDefs":[],"_type":"block","style":"normal","level":1,"listItem":"bullet"},{"_key":"05765810369b","children":[{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"You can now also see which file other users are in from the filetree. *","_key":"05765810369b0"}],"markDefs":[],"_type":"block","style":"normal","level":1,"listItem":"bullet"},{"_key":"78bf724759db","children":[{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"New dotfiles features:","_key":"78bf724759db0"}],"markDefs":[],"_type":"block","style":"normal","level":1,"listItem":"bullet"},{"_key":"ef5d811889c6","children":[{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"nix repls can now use ","_key":"ef5d811889c60"},{"_type":"span","marks":["code"],"text":"~/${REPL_SLUG}/.config","_key":"ef5d811889c61"},{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":" to store their dotfiles / config files in a ","_key":"ef5d811889c62"},{"_type":"span","marks":["1c6670476730"],"text":"XDG Base Directory Specification","_key":"ef5d811889c63"},{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"-compliant way.","_key":"ef5d811889c64"}],"markDefs":[{"_key":"1c6670476730","_type":"link","href":"https://specifications.freedesktop.org/basedir-spec/basedir-spec-latest.html"}],"_type":"block","style":"normal","level":2,"listItem":"bullet"},{"_key":"e7560739365f","children":[{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"ssh and fluxbox dotfiles are now available at ","_key":"e7560739365f0"},{"_type":"span","marks":["code"],"text":"~/${REPL_SLUG}/.config/{ssh,fluxbox}","_key":"e7560739365f1"},{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":" respectively for all repls, nix or non-nix.","_key":"e7560739365f2"}],"markDefs":[],"_type":"block","style":"normal","level":2,"listItem":"bullet"},{"_key":"9f01d10dab08","children":[{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"Have you ever had the urge to download one, single file from a repl? Now you can! Just click on the three dots next to file name and hit ‘Download’ to download your file.","_key":"9f01d10dab080"}],"markDefs":[],"_type":"block","style":"normal","level":1,"listItem":"bullet"},{"_key":"c6c1b16ec302","children":[{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"User experience changes","_key":"c6c1b16ec3020"}],"markDefs":[],"_type":"block","style":"h1"},{"_key":"8c60e7eecf66","children":[{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"We rolled out an updated profile experience. Visit any replit user's profile to see their showcased repls. We really like this ","_key":"8c60e7eecf660"},{"_type":"span","marks":["72967a265fef"],"text":"one","_key":"8c60e7eecf661"},{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"!","_key":"8c60e7eecf662"}],"markDefs":[{"_key":"72967a265fef","_type":"link","href":"https://replit.com/@LeviathanCoding?showcase=2"}],"_type":"block","style":"normal","level":1,"listItem":"bullet"},{"_key":"e24b3c6c74fa","children":[{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"The Packages tab has been updated with a fresh coat of paint. Information is now more contextual and notifications happen inline.","_key":"e24b3c6c74fa0"}],"markDefs":[],"_type":"block","style":"normal","level":1,"listItem":"bullet"},{"_key":"528135854dc6","children":[{"_type":"span","marks":["code"],"text":".replit","_key":"528135854dc60"},{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":" and Secrets overrides are now evaluated more consistently in more places. In increasing order of priority: ","_key":"528135854dc61"}],"markDefs":[],"_type":"block","style":"normal","level":1,"listItem":"bullet"},{"_key":"9821bc44107c","children":[{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"The OS environment:","_key":"9821bc44107c0"}],"markDefs":[],"_type":"block","style":"normal","level":2,"listItem":"bullet"},{"_key":"8d5e06539463","children":[{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"The environment baked into Polygott","_key":"8d5e065394630"}],"markDefs":[],"_type":"block","style":"normal","level":3,"listItem":"bullet"},{"_key":"b24fd3ec6011","children":[{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"The environment injected by Docker","_key":"b24fd3ec60110"}],"markDefs":[],"_type":"block","style":"normal","level":3,"listItem":"bullet"},{"_key":"c6e460fc2343","children":[{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"The nix environment","_key":"c6e460fc23430"}],"markDefs":[],"_type":"block","style":"normal","level":2,"listItem":"bullet"},{"_key":"17f178c3170d","children":[{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"The ","_key":"17f178c3170d0"},{"_type":"span","marks":["code"],"text":".replit","_key":"17f178c3170d1"},{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":" file","_key":"17f178c3170d2"}],"markDefs":[],"_type":"block","style":"normal","level":2,"listItem":"bullet"},{"_key":"464d36fe34e8","children":[{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"Secrets","_key":"464d36fe34e80"}],"markDefs":[],"_type":"block","style":"normal","level":2,"listItem":"bullet"},{"_key":"a5c6c33a9993","children":[{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"Bug fixes","_key":"a5c6c33a99930"}],"markDefs":[],"_type":"block","style":"h1"},{"_key":"fbcbaa7242d8","children":[{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"GitHub commits should now properly attribute changes to your GitHub account, and will use a privacy email when that setting is enabled on your GitHub account.","_key":"fbcbaa7242d80"}],"markDefs":[],"_type":"block","style":"normal","level":1,"listItem":"bullet"},{"_key":"fe300e44ddef","children":[{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"We cleaned up some extra blank space near the home screen header.","_key":"fe300e44ddef0"}],"markDefs":[],"_type":"block","style":"normal","level":1,"listItem":"bullet"},{"_key":"37125ea9415c","children":[{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"Fixes around deleting team repls.","_key":"37125ea9415c0"}],"markDefs":[],"_type":"block","style":"normal","level":1,"listItem":"bullet"},{"_key":"b83f6daccb54","children":[{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"The notification icon is back in its correct location.","_key":"b83f6daccb540"}],"markDefs":[],"_type":"block","style":"normal","level":1,"listItem":"bullet"},{"_key":"7c5a41854e3b","children":[{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"Deleting an open file could temporarily open a .env file.","_key":"7c5a41854e3b0"}],"markDefs":[],"_type":"block","style":"normal","level":1,"listItem":"bullet"},{"_key":"9db174123cf4","children":[{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"Users sessions expire much less frequently, keeping you logged into replit longer.","_key":"9db174123cf40"}],"markDefs":[],"_type":"block","style":"normal",